TopicTitle: I don't like the look of the new wings.

Articles.Content: They don't fit with stock... The big wings are thin and quite useless for larger planes. They are weird and curvy which kinda wanders from normal KSP designs.
i have a ton of things to criticize about 1.0 , but here i just HAVE TO disagree. I think that Porkjet dis a fantastic job with the wet wings. They look awesome on mk3 parts.
